data.description: Nicely updated 3BR, 2.5 Bath townhome in gated community. Spacious family room with lots of windows for natural sunlight. Kitchen overlooks dining/breakfast area. Stainless steel appliances. Upstairs huge primary suite with XL walk in closet. New fixtures, ceiling fans, door hardware, new energy efficient windows, roof, plumbing and 3 ply firewall. Fresh paint. Carport with workshop and plenty of room for 2 cars. Take out workshop and you can fit 3 cars. Front green area is part of condo unit. Great location tucked away in a quiet corner yet 1 minute walk to the pool. Easy access to I-10, Beltway 8, City Centre.
